---
title: Cheesy Mash Topped Beef and Red Wine Pie with Green Beans
description: A British favourite, cottage pie is most recognisable as a deeply savoury layer of meat filling topped with mash. Here, we're using beef mince and topping with cheesy mash as a twist. Best enjoyed after baking until golden and scrumptious!
